Paper: hep-th/0206109

Date: 2002-06-12

Title: Brane Probes, Toric Geometry, and Closed String Tachyons

Authors: Tapobrata Sarkar

Comments: 1+34 pages, LaTeX, final version to appear in NPB

Journal-ref: Nucl.Phys. B648 (2003) 497-522

We study non-supersymmetric orbifold singularities from the point of view ofD-brane probes. We present a description of the decay of such singularitiesfrom considerations of the toric geometry of the probe branes.